n February 9th, with registration pricing starting at $1499 CAD for the first 50 spots. Check out the site for more details, including the cancellation policy – which hopefully you won’t have to use. Not into gravel? The legendary BCBR 7 day MTB stage race will be held July 4-10.&nbsp;</span><span data-ez-name=\"bikerumor_com-medrectangle-3\"></span></p><p><a href=\"http://bcbrgravel.com/registration-details/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><em>bcbrgravel.com</em></a></p><p><a href=\"https://bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/BWR-Belgian-Waffle-Ride-Kansas-2021-October-announcement.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/BWR-Belgian-Waffle-Ride-Kansas-2021-October-announcement.jpg\" alt=\"BWR Kansas\" width=\"1128\" height=\"635\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1128px) 100vw, 1128px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb8 src ng ngcb8 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/BWR-Belgian-Waffle-Ride-Kansas-2021-October-announcement.jpg\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/BWR-Belgian-Waffle-Ride-Kansas-2021-October-announcement.jpg 1128w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/BWR-Belgian-Waffle-Ride-Kansas-2021-October-announcement-297x167.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/BWR-Belgian-Waffle-Ride-Kansas-2021-October-announcement-800x450.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/BWR-Belgian-Waffle-Ride-Kansas-2021-October-announcement-120x68.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/BWR-Belgian-Waffle-Ride-Kansas-2021-October-announcement-768x432.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-w