r 111 miles through the northeast with 8,000 feet of elevation gain.</p><p>BWR Kansas joins the existing BWR events including San Diego, CA (7/18), Asheville, NC (8/21), and Cedar City, UT (9/25). Check out all the details at the link below.</p><p><a href=\"https://belgianwaffleride.bike/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><em><span>belgianwaffleride.bike</span></em></a></p><h2>Leadville Trail 100 MTB</h2><p><a href=\"https://bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/MTB-Lottery-Social-Share-3.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/MTB-Lottery-Social-Share-3.jpg\" alt=\"Leadville Trail 100 MTB\" width=\"940\" height=\"788\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb8 src ng ngcb8 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/MTB-Lottery-Social-Share-3.jpg\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/MTB-Lottery-Social-Share-3.jpg 940w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/MTB-Lottery-Social-Share-3-297x249.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/MTB-Lottery-Social-Share-3-800x671.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/MTB-Lottery-Social-Share-3-120x101.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/MTB-Lottery-Social-Share-3-768x644.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/MTB-Lottery-Social-Share-3-696x583.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/MTB-Lottery-Social-Share-3-501x420.jpg 501w\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-